{"type": "article", "id": 4252, "title": "可换桌面的Adap.Table", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-10T07:52:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052332321aOX89NgWBtEZ3nd.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自比利时的设计师 Ta Yang Hsu 与南非设计师 Francois Elphick 近年来联手设计了不少产品，而两人最新带来的这款可变换的 Adap.Table 也于近日上线众筹网站 Indiegogo。若是想变换家居风格，就不得不重新涂装墙面以及换掉家居单品，而这次设计团队只想让你换一换桌面，Adap.Table 的桌脚以锁螺丝的方式固定桌面，不用钻洞，也无任何面积尺寸的限制，只要是一块四角形的平板便可。不管是透明的玻璃面板，还是原色模板，亦或是任何涂鸦创意的板材，几乎都能按照用户的需求随性创造。Adap.Table 本身选用了单一的黑色刚才，线条简洁利落，简约的工业风格适于创造各种居家风格的可能性。起售价 230 美元，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/adap-table-create-your-own-table-with-a-twist\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>，预计 2015 年 1 月出货。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233229WFj8VXx3kU5QvoRb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233230FxJ0MDwelho1U9tP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233230xv0SIZwpM34eYVLj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233231V2lHpgvOGme1kAJ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233231HTtN4hZ1sI0eaxAi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/ksr/assets/002/658/345/6abbc56c8f64cb84cac67566622a5f10_large.gif?1411981611\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}